---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ServiceSchema from '../components/ServiceSchema.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Groundworks Services | Surrey Contracting Limited"
  description="Professional groundworks contractor in Surrey, foundations, drainage, excavation, site preparation and concrete works."
  path="/groundworks"
  active="services"
>
  <ServiceSchema slot="head" name="Groundworks" slug="groundworks" description="Professional groundworks contractor in Surrey, foundations, drainage, excavation, site preparation and concrete works." />

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="page-hero-img" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/Trenching image.jpg')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <a href="/services">Services</a>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      <span>Groundworks</span>
    </nav>
    <h1 class="page-title">Groundworks Services</h1>
    <p class="page-lede">Professional groundworks contractor across Surrey, London and the South East.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Groundworks</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Expert groundworks from foundations to drainage.</h2>
      <p class="section-lede">Surrey Contracting offers a full range of groundworks services to residential and commercial clients across Surrey, London and the South East. With over 15 years of industry experience, you can be confident your project is in safe hands. At Surrey Contracting, health and safety is central to everything we do, and we continuously provide our staff with up-to-date training, ensuring every project is undertaken safely and efficiently.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/groundworks-foundations.webp')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Foundations &amp; Build to DPC</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Surrey Contracting provides complete foundation and build-to-DPC packages for residential, commercial and developer-led projects.Our works include excavation, foundation construction, concrete placement, brickwork and blockwork up to damp proof course level, substructure preparation and all associated groundwork requirements. We work to approved drawings, engineer specifications to ensure each plot or structure is built accurately and ready for the next phase of construction.From domestic extensions and new-build homes through to larger commercial and development schemes, our team delivers reliable substructure works with a strong focus on accuracy, programmes and quality control.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Strip foundations</li>
        <li>Trench fill foundations</li>
        <li>Block and Beam</li>
        <li>Raft foundations</li>
        <li>Concrete slabs</li>
        <li>Formwork, steel fixing, concrete works &amp; build to DPC</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/Surface water drainage.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Utility trenching &amp; Drainage</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Surrey Contracting delivers utilities trenching and drainage works for residential, commercial and developer-led projects across Surrey, London and the South East.Our services cover foul and surface water drainage, service trenches, ducting routes and below-ground infrastructure for water, electric and gas installations.We undertake soakaway construction, manhole and inspection chamber installation, pipework, service ducting and connections to existing drainage systems.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Foul &amp; surface water drainage</li>
        <li>Soakaway construction</li>
        <li>Manhole &amp; chamber installation</li>
        <li>Service ducting (gas, water, electric)</li>
        <li>Utility connections</li>
        <li>Building control compliance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/groundworks-siteprep.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Site Preparation</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">We offer comprehensive site preparation services using the latest equipment and machinery, ensuring your site is ready for the next phase of construction. This includes stripping topsoil and stockpiling for reuse, establishing site levels, installing temporary access roads and hardstanding areas, and carrying out any necessary ground stabilisation. Our site preparation works are planned carefully to minimise waste and maximise the reuse of materials on site.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Topsoil strip &amp; stockpiling</li>
        <li>Site levelling</li>
        <li>Temporary access roads</li>
        <li>Ground stabilisation</li>
        <li>Muck-away &amp; disposal</li>
        <li>Material reuse</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail svc-detail-alt">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid svc-detail-reverse">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/groundworks-excavation.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Excavations</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">With over a decade of operational success meeting the demands of our clients, our excavation services cover everything from small residential digs to large commercial schemes. We operate a range of excavators from 1.5-tonne mini diggers for restricted access work through to 30-tonne machines for major earthmoving operations. All our operators are fully trained, qualified and insured, ensuring safe and efficient operation on every site.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Residential excavations</li>
        <li>Commercial excavations</li>
        <li>Pond &amp; Lake excavation</li>
        <li>Bulk earthmoving</li>
        <li>Pool &amp; lake excavations</li>
        <li>Qualified &amp; insured operators</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-detail">
  <div class="container svc-detail-grid">
    <div class="svc-detail-media">
      <div class="svc-detail-photo" style="background-image:url('/assets/img/services/groundworks-agricultural.jpg')"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-detail-copy">
      <h2 class="section-title">Agricultural Groundworks</h2>
      <p class="lede-dark">Surrey Contracting provides specialist agricultural groundworks services including new access track installation, surface water drainage systems, fencing and gates, yard concreting and land improvement works. We understand the unique requirements of agricultural clients and work around seasonal schedules to minimise disruption to farming operations.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Access track installation</li>
        <li>Surface water drainage</li>
        <li>Fencing &amp; gates</li>
        <li>Yard concreting</li>
        <li>Land improvement</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container cta-strip-row">
    <div>
      <h3>Got a groundworks project to discuss?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-strip-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow">Request a quote</a>
      <a href="tel:01932932650" class="btn btn-ghost-light">01932 932650</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
